				\begin{document}$$G_{{{\text{N}}_{2} - {\text{N}}_{2} {\text{H}}}}$$\end{document}) as descriptors to rule out ASCs with low activity. In the second step, the descriptors were the free energy for NH3 desorption and the hydrogenation from –NH2 to –NH3 (ΔGNH2-NH3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
